com.fs.starfarer.api.impl.campaign.ids

Class MemFlags

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.fs.starfarer.api.impl.campaign.ids.MemFlags

  • public class MemFlags
extends java.lang.Object
    Variable names for stuff stored in memory that: 1) Generally is used more than once in code, so it's convenient to track from here. These may or may not be used in rules.csv.

    Alex Mosolov Copyright 2014 Fractal Softworks, LLC
